HEADWORD: Recess
<hw>Re*cess"</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[G.]</ety> <def>A decree of the
imperial diet of the old German empire.</def> <rj><au>Brande &
C.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Recessed</ent>⟦br⟧
